rl":"https://api.github.com/users/butonic/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/butonic/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/butonic/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/butonic/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/butonic/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/butonic/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/butonic/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/butonic/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/butonic/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-04-05t12:51:45z","updated_at":"2013-04-05t12:51:45z","body":"i cannot reproduce this in oc 5.0.3 & master. uploading a file named \"document with ' in filename.txt\" via the upload button and d'n'd works fine with chromium and the mirall sync client in ubuntu 12.10\r\n\r\ncould you state how exactly you are trying to upload? what is the exact filename? what browser are you using? what os? please use our [template](https://raw.github.com/owncloud/core/master/issue_template.md) and review the [guidelines for contributing](https://github.com/owncloud/core/blob/master/contributing.md) to this repository."},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/15958155","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/2731#issuecomment-15958155","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/2731","id":15958155,"user":{"login":"offerman","id":3305099,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/81d4eeef6db236ff127f74f5bc56f55f?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f8d6c13b2df73252d1d976692cdaa2487.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"81d4eeef6db236ff127f74f5bc56f55f","url":"https://api.github.com/users/offerman","html_url":"https://github.com/offerman","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/offerman/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/offerman/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/offerman/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/offerman/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/offerman/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/offerman/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/offerman/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/offerman/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/offerman/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-04-05t14:18:22z","updated_at":"2013-04-05t14:18:22z","body":"did some further investigation and found that mod_security (mod_security-2.7.1-3.el6.x86_64 on centos 6.3) was blocking the upload:\r\n\r\n[fri apr 05 15:45:54 2013] [error] [client ***:****:****:1:d63d:7eff:fe4c:a94c] modsecurity: access denied with code 44 (phase 2). match of \"eq 0\" against \"multipart_strict_error\" required. [file \"/etc/httpd/conf.d/mod_security.conf\"] [line \"34\"] [id \"200002\"] [msg \"multipart request body     failed strict validation:     pe 0,     bq 0,     bw 0,     db 0,     da 0,     hf 0,     lf 0,     sm 0,     iq 1,     ip 0,     ih 0,     fl 0\"] [hostname \"owncloud.********.***\"] [uri \"/index.php/apps/files/ajax/upload.php\"] [unique_id \"uv7vyco4qgoaaeuswxyaaaar\"]\r\n\r\nso i disabled rule 200002 in my httpd configuration:\r\n  <ifmodule mod_security2.c>\r\n  secruleremovebyid 200002\r\n  </ifmodule>\r\n\r\nfiles now uploading without a glitch :]"},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/15960999","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/2731#issuecomment-15960999","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/2731","id":15960999,"user":{"login":"sergnl","id":4036024,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/ad8d4e38b6fd5d951219c84089f693b4?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f62c29caa1e713e3beccbdb25b429a7cf.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"ad8d4e38b6fd5d951219c84089f693b4","url":"http